data.title: Paul Mullin - Wrexham
data.meta_description: Profile page for Wrexham football player Paul Mullin (Striker). Born on November 6th, 1994 in Liverpool, England. See Paul Mullin's bio, transfer history and stats here.
data.text:
Mullin earns Morecambe deal

Teenage striker Paul Mullin has been rewarded with a new contract at Morecambe following his fine start to the season.

13/09/14 4:46pm

Mullin set for new deal

Sky Sports understands Morecambe have offered highly-rated striker Paul Mullin a new deal just a month after signing him.

12/09/14 12:13pm
